title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - MSFS roadmap - world update 15 and new aircrafts
description:
In this video we will look at the roadmap updates which were made available for MSFS 2020. We will go through the updated bug and wish list and have a look at what will be the next world update which will be released as well as 2 new aircrafts from which one of them will likely come pretty soon.
